esponsive_content-320.avif 320w, https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/9d06f8ebe02f/97e2ee85b61f/responsive_content-640.avif 640w, https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/9d06f8ebe02f/97e2ee85b61f/responsive_content-960.avif 960w, https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/9d06f8ebe02f/97e2ee85b61f/responsive_content-1440.avif 1440w&#34; sizes=&#34;(min-width: 1024px) 864px, (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 64px), calc(100vw - 32px)&#34;&gt;&lt;source type=&#34;image/webp&#34; data-srcset=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/9d06f8ebe02f/97e2ee85b61f/responsive_content-320.webp 320w, https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/9d06f8ebe02f/97e2ee85b61f/responsive_content-640.webp 640w, https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/9d06f8ebe02f/97e2ee85b61f/responsive_content-960.webp 960w, https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/9d06f8ebe02f/97e2ee85b61f/responsive_content-1440.webp 1440w&#34; sizes=&#34;(min-width: 1024px) 864px, (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 64px), calc(100vw - 32px)&#34;&gt;&lt;img&#xA;    src=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/9d06f8ebe02f/97e2ee85b61f/responsive_content-placeholder-64.jpg&#34;&#xA;    width=&#34;320&#34;&#xA;    height=&#34;174&#34;&#xA;    data-srcset=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/9d06f8ebe02f/97e2ee85b61f/responsive_content-fallback-320.jpg 320w, https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/9d06f8ebe02f/97e2ee85b61f/responsive_content-fallback-640.jpg 640w, https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/9d06f8ebe02f/97e2ee85b61f/responsive_content-fallback-960.jpg 960w, https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/9d06f8ebe02f/97e2ee85b61f/responsive_content-fallback-1440.jpg 1440w&#34;&#xA;    data-src=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/9d06f8ebe02f/97e2ee85b61f/responsive_content-fallback-320.jpg&#34;&#xA;    data-native-src=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/9d06f8ebe02f/97e2ee85b61f/responsive_content-fallback-320.jpg&#34;&#xA;    data-native-srcset=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/9d06f8ebe02f/97e2ee85b61f/responsive_content-fallback-320.jpg 320w, https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/9d06f8ebe02f/97e2ee85b61f/responsive_content-fallback-640.jpg 640w, https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/9d06f8ebe02f/97e2ee85b61f/responsive_content-fallback-960.jpg 960w, https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/9d06f8ebe02f/97e2ee85b61f/responsive_content-fallback-1440.jpg 1440w&#34;&#xA;    sizes=&#34;(min-width: 1024px) 864px, (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 64px), calc(100vw - 32px)&#34;&#xA;    loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&#xA;    decoding=&#34;async&#34;&#xA;    fetchpriority=&#34;low&#34;&#xA;    alt=&#34;alt text&#34;&#xA;    data-image-state=&#34;loading&#34;&#xA;    class=&#34;gallery-image stack-lazy-image&#34;&#xA;    data-lazy-image=&#34;true&#34; data-lazy-state=&#34;preview&#34;&#xA;    data-lightbox-enabled=&#34;true&#34;&#xA;    data-lightbox-strategy=&#34;eager&#34;&#xA;    data-lightbox-avif=&#34;/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/9d06f8ebe02f/97e2ee85b61f/responsive_content-320.avif 320w, /2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/9d06f8ebe02f/97e2ee85b61f/responsive_content-640.avif 640w, /2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/9d06f8ebe02f/97e2ee85b61f/responsive_content-960.avif 960w, /2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/9d06f8ebe02f/97e2ee85b61f/responsive_content-1440.avif 1440w&#34;&#xA;    data-lightbox-webp=&#34;/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/9d06f8ebe02f/97e2ee85b61f/responsive_content-320.webp 320w, /2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/9d06f8ebe02f/97e2ee85b61f/responsive_content-640.webp 640w, /2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/9d06f8ebe02f/97e2ee85b61f/responsive_content-960.webp 960w, /2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/9d06f8ebe02f/97e2ee85b61f/responsive_content-1440.webp 1440w&#34;&#xA;    data-lightbox-fallback=&#34;/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/9d06f8ebe02f/97e2ee85b61f/responsive_content-fallback-1440.jpg&#34; data-flex-basis=&#34;441px&#34; data-flex-grow=&#34;184&#34;&gt;&lt;/picture&gt;&lt;/span&gt;相信你也注意到了，在流出流量这一块cdn回源流出流量比外网流出流量便宜，也就是说有更省钱的方法，那就是在我们访问由cdn加速的域名的时候，cdn会回源oss取资源，计费按0.15元/GB，并且阿里云的esa（cdn的上位替代）是有免费版的，最重要的是只有cdn没有缓存或缓存过期的时候才会回源到oss，其他时候都是直接返回内容的，大大降低了流量消耗&lt;br&gt;&#xA;按每小时计费一次，月底如果不足0.01就直接抹零，现在计算一下我的一个月的阿里云账单，域名每一个月39/12=3.25元，esa0元，oss存储0.0000012938x730=0.000944474元，流量(320÷1024)×(20%×0.5+80%×0.15)=0.06875元，请求0元，所以合计起来每个月网站运营成本约为4元&lt;/p&gt;</description>
